37246>>>>>    
37246>>>>>    
37246>>>>>    //
37246>>>>>    // This procedure is called when validating a session and after logging in. Its purpose is to 
37246>>>>>    // update properties based on the session and user data. Augment this function to update 
37246>>>>>    // properties based on the session / user table. Note that WebAppUser and WebAppSession contain
37246>>>>>    // the right records when this procedure is called.
37246>>>>>    //
37246>>>>>    // Params:
37246>>>>>    //      bClear   True if the procedure is called before session validation to clear properties.
37246>>>>>    //
37246>>>>>    Procedure UpdateSessionProperties Boolean bClear
37248>>>>>        Handle hoUserDD
37248>>>>>        
37248>>>>>        Get phoUserDD to hoUserDD
37249>>>>>        
37249>>>>>        //  Update user properties
37249>>>>>        If (not(bClear) and HasRecord(hoUserDD)) Begin
37251>>>>>            Set psUsername to (Trim(WebAppUser.FullName))
37252>>>>>            Set psLoginName to (Trim(WebAppUser.LoginName))
37253>>>>>            Set piUserRights to WebAppUser.Rights
37254>>>>>            
37254>>>>>            Send OnSessionPropertiesSet 
37255>>>>>        End
37255>>>>>>
37255>>>>>        Else Begin
37256>>>>>            Set psUsername to ""
37257>>>>>            Set psLoginName to ""
37258>>>>>            Set piUserRights to 0
37259>>>>>            
37259>>>>>            Send OnSessionPropertiesClear
37260>>>>>        End
37260>>>>>>
37260>>>>>    End_Procedure
37261>>>>>    
37261>>>>>    Procedure OnSessionPropertiesSet
37263>>>>>        //  Empty event stub
37263>>>>>    End_Procedure
37264>>>>>    
37264>>>>>    Procedure OnSessionPropertiesClear
37266>>>>>        //  Empty event stub
37266>>>>>    End_Procedure
37267>>>>>    
37267>>>>>    Procedure EndSession
37269>>>>>        Integer iErr
37269>>>>>        Boolean bLogWebSession
37269>>>>>        Handle hoSessionDD       
37269>>>>>        
37269>>>>>        Get phoSessionDD to hoSessionDD
37270>>>>>        Get pbLogWebSession to bLogWebSession
37271>>>>>        If not bLogWebSession Begin
37273>>>>>            Forward Send EndSession
37275>>>>>            Procedure_Return
37276>>>>>        End
37276>>>>>>
37276>>>>>            
37276>>>>>        //  Check if session exists
37276>>>>>        Send Clear of hoSessionDD
37277>>>>>        Get psSessionKey to WebAppSession.SessionKey
37278>>>>>        
37278>>>>>        Send Find of hoSessionDD EQ Index.1
37279>>>>>        If (Found) Begin
37281>>>>>            Set Field_Changed_Value of hoSessionDD Field WebAppSession.Active to "N"
37282>>>>>            Get Request_Validate of hoSessionDD to iErr
37283>>>>>            If (iErr) Begin
37285>>>>>                // this should not happen. If it does its a programming error
37285>>>>>                Error DFERR_PROGRAM C_$WebAppSessionValidateFailed
37286>>>>>>
37286>>>>>                Procedure_Return
37287>>>>>            End
37287>>>>>>
37287>>>>>            Send Request_Save of hoSessionDD
37288>>>>>        End
37288>>>>>>
37288>>>>>    End_Procedure
37289>>>>>
37289>>>>>End_Class
